7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Drift and Freshdesk (Freddy AI) share a solid foundation of core features including Live Chat, Ai Chatbot, Analytics, Multichannel. On the other hand, Freshdesk (Freddy AI) uniquely offers Ticket Management and Knowledge Base and Self Service and Voice Support, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Drift holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Freshdesk (Freddy AI) scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Drift and Freshdesk (Freddy AI) offer flexible pricing models. Freshdesk (Freddy AI) stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Drift requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
