b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Drift is best suited for B2B sales teams, demand generation, enterprise marketing, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Freshdesk (Freddy AI), meanwhile, shines for growing businesses, IT service desks, support teams, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2015, Drift describes itself as \"Conversational AI platform for sales and customer engagement on websites.\" Freshdesk (Freddy AI), established in 2010, positions itself as \"Customer support platform with Freddy AI for automated ticket resolution.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Freshdesk (Freddy AI)** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to more features (10 vs 6), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Drift is a poor choice — far from it. Drift excels in its own right, particularly for B2B sales teams and demand generation.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value good free plan for small teams, go with Freshdesk (Freddy AI). If excellent for b2b lead qualification matters more to you, Drift is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
